// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2168 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 3e0b380a-9c30-53d2-a7f9-dcdb7ba16335

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*")
